quote.summary: Suzhou Novosense Microelectronics Co Ltd is a China-based company mainly engaged in the research and development, design and sales of analog chips. The Company's products cover sensors, signal chains and power management, and are used in the automotive, pan-energy and consumer electronics fields. The Company's sensor products mainly include magnetic sensors, pressure sensors, temperature and humidity sensors, such as include integrated current sensors, linear current sensors, angle sensors, gauge pressure sensors, absolute pressure sensors, differential pressure sensors, analog output temperature sensors, digital output temperature sensors, temperature sensors and other products. Signal chain products include signal conditioning chips, isolators, interfaces, universal signal chains and other products. Power management products mainly include gate drivers, power supplies and other products. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in the domestic market.
